msgid ""
"<span> This agreement shall be effective from the day it is signed by the two parties and ends either at the end of the litigation procedure entrusted to the First Party / or with the First Party ceasing from  defending on behalf of the Second Party In the event that he/she breaches the fees clause mentioned in the scope of work subject of this Agreement and in accordance with the provisions of Article (6) of this agreement. The First Party has the right to terminate the agreement of its own unilateral will at any stage of the lawsuit.\n"
"          </span>"
msgstr ""
"<span> This agreement shall be effective from the day it is signed by the two parties and ends either at the end of the litigation procedure entrusted to the First Party / or with the First Party ceasing from  defending on behalf of the Second Party In the event that he/she breaches the fees clause mentioned in the scope of work subject of this الاتفاقية and in accordance with the provisions of Article (6) of this agreement. The First Party has the right to terminate the agreement of its own unilateral will at any stage of the lawsuit.\n"
